tail. It does not feel pain if its tail is bitten."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Although slow, it is skilled at fishing with its tail. It does not feel pain if its tail is bitten."},{"version":"x","text":"It is always vacantly lost in thought, but no one knows what it is thinking about. It is good at fishing with its tail."},{"version":"y","text":"It lazes vacantly near water. If something bites its tail, it won\u2019t even notice for a whole day."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Slowpoke uses its tail to catch prey by dipping it in water at the side of a river. However, this Pok\u00e9mon often forgets what it\u2019s doing and often spends entire days just loafing at water\u2019s edge."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Slowpoke uses its tail to catch prey by dipping it in water at the side of a river. However, this Pok\u00e9mon often forgets what it\u2019s doing and often spends entire days just loafing at water\u2019s edge."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its long tail often breaks off. It doesn\u2019t really feel any pain, though, and the tail grows back, so Slowpoke isn\u2019t particularly bothered."},{"version":"moon","text":"Alolan home cooking involves drying Slowpoke tails and then simmering them into a salty stew."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"There are some places where Slowpoke is worshiped because of a long-standing belief that whenever Slowpoke yawns, it rains."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Although their tails, which fall off naturally, can easily be found lying around, they\u2019re a precious ingredient for cooking."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Incredibly slow and sluggish. It is quite content to loll about without worrying about the time."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Incredibly slow and sluggish. It is quite content to loll about without worrying about the time."},{"version":"sword","text":"Slow-witted and oblivious, this Pok\u00e9mon won\u2019t feel any pain if its tail gets eaten. It won\u2019t notice when its tail grows back, either."},{"version":"shield","text":"When this Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s tail is soaked in water, sweetness seeps from it. Slowpoke uses this trait to lure in and fish up other Pok\u00e9mon."}],"evo":{"name":"slowpoke","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"slowbro","level":1,"min_level":37,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"slowking","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"trade","item":null,"held_item":"kings-rock","known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/79.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/79.png","capture":190,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"hp":1},"forms":[{"id":10164,"name":"slowpoke-galar","sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/10164.png"}]}